               <text>NeoBenz® <content styleCode="italics">Micro</content> is supplied as follows:<br/>SIZE: 45 gram tube<br/>NDC NUMBER:<br/>(3.5% benzoyl peroxide cream): 67402-020-45<br/>(5.5% benzoyl peroxide cream): 67402-021-45<br/>
